docs.abstract: Windows 10 does not support the Windows XP Mode that came with some versions of Windows 7, but a virtual machine can circumvent the issue.
docs.snippet: Windows 10 does not support the Windows XP Mode that came with some versions of Windows 7, but a virtual machine can circumvent the issue.
docs.lead_paragraph: Q. I use XP Mode on my Windows 7 Professional edition machine to run older programs. I’m considering upgrading to Windows 10 and would like to know if XP Mode is available in that operating system.

docs.abstract: An article in the journal Science reported a type of machine learning that outperformed human capabilities for a narrow range of vision-related tasks.
docs.snippet: An article in the journal Science reported a type of machine learning that outperformed human capabilities for a narrow range of vision-related tasks.
docs.lead_paragraph: Computer researchers reported artificial-intelligence advances on Thursday that surpassed human capabilities for a narrow set of vision-related tasks.

headline.main: A Learning Advance in Artificial Intelligence Rivals Human Abilities
headline.print_headline: An Advance in Artificial Intelligence Rivals Human Vision Abilities

docs.abstract: Microsoft gives you a way to see what Windows Update has downloaded and installed on your PC.
docs.snippet: Microsoft gives you a way to see what Windows Update has downloaded and installed on your PC.
docs.lead_paragraph: Q. I know Windows 10 automatically performs software updates, but when I get a notification saying, “Updates were installed,” I’d like to know what exactly was installed. Is there a way to find out?

headline.main: How to See What Windows 10 Just Installed

docs.abstract: The authorities said the chip maker had abused its dominant market position in the region by offering financial incentives to smartphone and tablet manufacturers.
docs.snippet: The authorities said the chip maker had abused its dominant market position in the region by offering financial incentives to smartphone and tablet manufacturers.
docs.lead_paragraph: The European Commission on Tuesday filed antitrust charges against the chip maker Qualcomm, the latest in a growing number of competition investigations targeting American technology companies.

headline.main: Qualcomm Is Accused of Violating Antitrust Rules in Europe

docs.abstract: The former Microsoft executive explains why Microsoft appears to have fallen behind Sony in the game console market.
docs.snippet: The former Microsoft executive explains why Microsoft appears to have fallen behind Sony in the game console market.
docs.lead_paragraph: SEATTLE — Robbie Bach has felt the highs and lows of the video game business.

headline.main: Former Xbox Chief Robbie Bach on Console Battles
headline.print_headline: Inside the Battle of the Consoles

docs.abstract: The company joins Google, Facebook and others in disclosing when users of email and other services have probably been targeted by hackers working on behalf of governments.
docs.snippet: The company joins Google, Facebook and others in disclosing when users of email and other services have probably been targeted by hackers working on behalf of governments.
docs.lead_paragraph: SEATTLE — Microsoft says it will begin notifying users of its online services if they have been targets of suspected state-sponsored online attacks, joining a growing list of Internet companies stepping up their security policies with similar measures.

headline.main: Microsoft to Notify Users of Government Hackings
headline.print_headline: Microsoft to Notify Users of Government Hackings

docs.abstract: Faster broadband speeds and bigger hard drives in game consoles are changing the way the video game business works.
docs.snippet: Faster broadband speeds and bigger hard drives in game consoles are changing the way the video game business works.
docs.lead_paragraph: SEATTLE — This holiday season could be remembered as a digital watershed for the games business, the moment when the old way of selling video games — on discs in boxes — finally gave way to downloads.

headline.main: As Downloads Take Over, a Turning Point for the Video Game Industry
headline.print_headline: Video Game Downloads Transform the State of Play
